{
  "stem": "21139.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But it was very pretty, very nice.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we used to-- there was a small area downstairs where we could-- children-- where we could play.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And-- but my mother didn't like me to run around there to play.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "She wanted me in the synagogue with her to pray, and she was very strict about that.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But there were times when we used to go there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But as I said before, there were very few children there, I-- because it was a big Jewish community many years before.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But I don't remember those times.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At the time when you were a child going to that synagogue, about how many people were there who were going?",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Not many.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Maybe 20, 25.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It-- it was not packed anymore as I understand it was years ago.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "As I said, I grew up in a time-- abnormal times, and where nothing was the way it used to be.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Can you tell me about the rabbi?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "His name was Mr.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was a cantor.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was-- he officiated at funerals.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Weddings, there weren't any.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Bar mitzvahs, there weren't any.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the last bar mitzvah was my brother Julius.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I remember that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But he-- my family came from out of town who lived in Pforzheim.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And there were very few people.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "The people from Konigsbach came.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And there was just at home a little bit of a celebration.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was always very special, because, as I said, my mother was very religious.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And a holiday, it was so beautiful.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we had a dining area next to the kitchen.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that was set up with white tablecloth, the best china.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it was so festive.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And even though we had no luxuries and we just had-- we had food.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
